::: text-justify
Welcome!

I am a sociologist and demographer based at [IRIS](https://iris.ehess.fr/) (Inserm, Université Sorbonne Paris Nord), where I hold a Junior Professor Chair on "health inequalities". My work focuses on health inequalities in relation to gender and (paid and unpaid) work. I am also affiliated with the [Health Inequalities, Life Course and Ageing Group](https://www.kcl.ac.uk/research/institute-of-gerontology) and with the [Global Institute for Women's Leadership](https://www.kcl.ac.uk/giwl) at King's College London.

You can find my detailed CV [here](https://github.com/constance-beaufils/cv/blob/main/CV_Beaufils_EN_1225.pdf).
:::

